p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Rewards 2023 l&agrave; ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh ghi nh\u1eadn v&agrave; trao th\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng kh&aacute;ch \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng v&igrave; s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle Saigon.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1eb7t ngay v&agrave; \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m! \u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin chi ti\u1ebft, vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n h\u1ec7 qua s\u1ed1 (84) 2838 234 999 Ext: 27515 ho\u1eb7c email: caravelle.rewards@caravellehotel.com!<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 488px;top: 54.5625px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48in5n6u fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/7cb28096abfa8b0c0fe5aefa885b506f_Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle-Rewards-Banner-1\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-6gsukki0 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed4I \u0110I\u1ec2M<\/h3>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 260px;top: 37.375px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-6gsub7qa fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>VN D 3,000,000 ++ = 01 \u0110I\u1ec2M<\/strong><br \/>&Aacute;p d\u1ee5ng cho Booking th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">--------------<br \/><strong>QUY\u1ec0N L\u1ee2I TH&Agrave;NH VI&Ecirc;N<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ec9 &aacute;p d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng kh&aacute;ch nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m<br \/>Khi \u0111\u0103ng k&yacute; tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ebd c&oacute; nh\u1eefng quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Gi\u1ea3m 15% tr&ecirc;n gi&aacute; t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c&oacute;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Gi\u1ea3m 15% d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Spa, Gi\u1eb7t \u1ee7i v&agrave; F&amp;B<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Gi\u1ea3m 10% cho s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n ti\u1ec7c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">01 b&aacute;nh sinh nh\u1eadt 22cm nh&acirc;n ng&agrave;y sinh nh\u1eadt th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">05 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho m\u1ed7i th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n \u0111\u0103ng k&yacute; m\u1edbi&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 437px;top: 265.875px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5gamkh10 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Rewards-2023-Eflyer.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">XEM CHI TI\u1ebeT<\/span><\/a><\/div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-6gsu9tmm fg-image  img-responsive 