;c th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c li&ecirc;n quan t\u1edbi t&agrave;i kho\u1ea3n H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; B\u1ea3n tin v&agrave; khuy\u1ebfn m&atilde;i h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; quy\u1ec1n s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i c&aacute;c quy t\u1eafc, gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n, quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; c&aacute;c \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n b&aacute;o tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngo&agrave;i ra, Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; quy\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh gi&aacute; tr\u1ecb \u0110i\u1ec3m CR khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n &aacute;nh s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v&agrave; ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh CR b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n&agrave;o.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed4I \u0110I\u1ec2M:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra s\u1ed1 d\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m CR v&agrave; \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m CR th&agrave;nh \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; G\u1eedi y&ecirc;u c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng email v&agrave; g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn caravelle.rewards@caravellehotel.com<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; \u0110i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u1edfng CR ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ed5i trong v&ograve;ng 01 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng&agrave;y H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n tr\u1ea3 ph&ograve;ng, \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb tr\u1eeb t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u1ecfi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n b&aacute;o tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&bull; Sau khi \u0111\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1edfng, h\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i cho c&aacute;c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v&agrave; d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n. H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n ph\u1ea3i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1eb5n c&oacute;.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">__________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>PHI\u1ebeU \u01afU \u0110&Atilde;I:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1eb5n c&oacute; t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m y&ecirc;u c\u1ea7u. Vui l&ograve;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v&agrave; D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n: Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr\u1ecb trong 06 th&aacute;ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng&agrave;y c\u1ea5p v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u1eeb khi c&oacute; quy \u0111\u1ecbnh kh&aacute;c. H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n nh\u1eadn Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i cho c&aacute;c S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v&agrave; D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n trong v&ograve;ng 05 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi\u1ec7c. H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n ph\u1ea3i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1eb5n c&oacute;. Phi\u1ebfu \u01b0u \u0111&atilde;i ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n, hay \u0111\u1ed5i th&agrave;nh \u0111i\u1ec3m v&agrave;o t&agrave;i kho\u1ea3n H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i th&agrave;nh ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">_________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TR&Aacute;CH NHI\u1ec6M C\u1ee6A H\u1ed8I VI&Ecirc;N:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n CR khi \u0111\u1eb7t ph&ograve;ng. H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb t&agrave;i kho\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v\u1edbi B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u1ebb H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n CR trong v&ograve;ng 60 ng&agrave;y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng&agrave;y tr\u1ea3 ph&ograve;ng. N\u1ebfu kh&ocirc;ng, c&aacute;c \u0111i\u1ec3m CR li&ecirc;n quan s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i n&agrave;o v\u1ec1 \u0110i\u1ec3m CR b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t c&oacute; th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u1ebb H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n CR qua email. Khi h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o t\u1edbi B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u1ebb H\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n CR b\u1eb1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n. \u0110i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5i khi h\u1ed9i vi&ecirc;n r&uacute;t kh\u1ecfi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48in5n6l{ \npadding-top: 20px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-5gamkh10 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ \ncolor:#ffffff;\n}\n.ffb-id-5gamkh10 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ \ncolor:#ffffff;\n}\n.ffb-id-5gamkh10 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ \nborder-color: transparent;\n}\n.ffb-id-5gamkh10 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{